---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const packages = [
  { name: '@fzagent/core', desc: 'tipos Zod, logger, config loader, event bus' },
  { name: '@fzagent/providers', desc: 'multi-LLM com fallback, OAuth Anthropic, Gemini CLI, OpenRouter free' },
  { name: '@fzagent/memory', desc: 'embeddings ONNX BGE-base, Qdrant, Wiki SQLite + FTS5' },
  { name: '@fzagent/agent', desc: 'budget loop, state machine, circuit breaker, builtins, heartbeat' },
  { name: '@fzagent/skills', desc: 'auto-discovery genaisrc/*.genai.mjs' },
  { name: '@fzagent/cli', desc: 'binario fzagent (commander)' },
];
---

<Base title="API reference">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>API reference</h1>
    <p>
      Cada pacote do monorepo expoe uma superficie publica via barrel exports.
      A documentacao completa e gerada via <code>tsc --declaration</code> e fica em
      <code>packages/&lt;name&gt;/dist/index.d.ts</code>.
    </p>

    <h2>Pacotes</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Pacote</th><th>Descricao</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {packages.map((p) => (
          <tr>
            <td><code>{p.name}</code></td>
            <td>{p.desc}</td>
          </tr>
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>TODO</h2>
    <p>
      Geracao automatica de paginas por simbolo via <code>typedoc</code>
      ou <code>api-extractor</code>. Por enquanto, leia os arquivos
      <code>.d.ts</code> em <code>dist/</code> ou as fontes em <code>src/</code>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
